Your task is to generate an equal superposition of all 2_N_ basis vectors on _N_ qubits:

![](https://espresso.codeforces.com/3ce44b5f49a946ba7ddef181f4073d7d0aa6c397.png)

For example,

*   for _N_ = 1, the required state is simply ![](https://espresso.codeforces.com/d8efee248abd35b37efa370723867c58ea1636d2.png),
